display_long_description:
An arcade style mathematics brain teaser set to chill music!

To begin, there are two gameplay modes, Random or Challenge.

1. If you select Random, you may choose either a 3x3 or 4x4 board size. 

2. If you select Challenge, choose 1 of 10 prebuilt "Challenge" boards from the dropdown menu.

When ready, hit Play!    

In both modes you are provided a number you have and a number you want to get to.  To complete a round, Use the buttons on the board to navigate to the goal value.  In Random mode the goal is to complete the most rounds possible.  In Challenge mode you compete to use the least buttons pressed.

A top 20 leaderboard is provided after each game to show how you stack up against the competition.  Show your friends or parents that you've got the Super Big Brain!

Key Features: 
 - 4 functions available (add, subtract, multiply, divide)
 - 3x3 and 4x4 game board sizes
 - 10 different music beats
 - Play up to 20 rounds each random game
 - Random hidden time bonuses to find
 - Leaderboards for each game board size and mode
